2620 IF ALICE_SIZE = 2 THEN PRINT "THE KEY FITS BUT YOU ARE MUCH TOO" : PRINT "BIG TO FIT THROUGH THE DOOR!" : GOTO 2000
2630 IF ALICE_SIZE = 3 THEN PRINT "YOU CANNOT EVEN KNEEL TO REACH THE" : PRINT "TINY DOOR AT THIS SIZE!" : GOTO 2000
3000 REM ============================================
3010 REM  ROOM 3: THE GARDEN PATH
3020 REM ============================================
3030 PRINT "--- THE BEAUTIFUL GARDEN ---"
3040 PRINT "YOU STEP INTO A LOVELY GARDEN WITH"
3050 PRINT "BRIGHT FLOWER-BEDS AND COOL FOUNTAINS."
