3450 IF CATERPILLAR_MET = 1 THEN PRINT "AH, YOU AGAIN. REMEMBER: ONE SIDE MAKES" : PRINT "YOU TALLER, THE OTHER SIDE SHORTER." : GOTO 3600
3460 PRINT "(1) I HARDLY KNOW, SIR"
3470 PRINT "(2) I AM ALICE"
