3490 IF C = 1 THEN PRINT "HMPH. EXPLAIN YOURSELF." : PRINT "THE CATERPILLAR PUFFS SMOKE THOUGHTFULLY."
3500 IF C = 2 THEN PRINT "ALICE? WHAT ALICE? YOU DON'T LOOK LIKE" : PRINT "MUCH OF AN ANYTHING TO ME."
3510 PRINT
3520 PRINT "THE CATERPILLAR CRAWLS OFF THE MUSHROOM."
